<h1 class="hero-h">Gym grand opening <em style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;">checklist.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">The honest grand-opening playbook. Soft open first; grand open second; and then the 90 days that actually determine whether the gym makes it. T-30 day, T-14, T-7, day-of, and post-open punch lists — built for the first-time owner doing this for the first time.</p>
</div></div>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">The honest framing</span>
<h2 class="h2">Grand opening is the starting line, not the finish line</h2>
<p class="body">Most operators treat grand opening as the destination. It's not — it's the start of the 6-12 month working-capital survival window. The opening event matters; how you operate the next 90 days matters more.</p>
<p class="body">This checklist is sequenced to handle the opening well (so members start with a great experience) and to set up the post-open operating rhythm that determines whether the gym ramps to breakeven.</p>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">T-30 days</span>
<h2 class="h2">30 days before grand open</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Final certificate of occupancy confirmed; punch list complete</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>All equipment delivered, installed, tested, and member-ready</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Cleaning vendor contracted; first deep-clean scheduled 7 days before soft open</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Gym CRM + AI agent platform fully configured; lead nurture sequences live</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Payment processing tested end-to-end with a real transaction</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Staff hired, certified, and trained on member-facing systems</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Soft open invitation sent to founding members</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Press outreach: pitch local lifestyle/business outlets on grand opening</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Signage permits applied for (exterior signage often needs city sign-off)</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Insurance binders updated and active for grand-open date</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Final founding-member count vs target reviewed; gap-close push if behind</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Class schedule published 30 days out; member booking enabled</div></li>
</ul>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">T-14 days</span>
<h2 class="h2">Two weeks before</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Soft open begins — 7-14 days of founding-members-only access</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Daily standup with full team: what broke, what worked, what to fix</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Founding-member feedback collected after first 3 classes</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Locker room operations stress-tested at peak hours</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Check-in flow timed and refined for under-15-second member entry</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>AI agent conversation quality reviewed; tune anything that misses</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Grand-open marketing push goes live (Meta + Google + email)</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Press kit finalized and ready to send to media on opening day</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Branded apparel + opening-week swag delivered and inventoried</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Photographer/videographer booked for opening day content capture</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Coffee/water/refreshments for opening week confirmed</div></li>
</ul>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">T-7 days</span>
<h2 class="h2">One week before</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Final walkthrough with every staff member; everyone knows their role on day one</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Class instructors do dry-run of their opening-day class</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>All exterior signage installed and lit</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Member-facing app downloaded and tested by 10+ founding members</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Grand-open email sent to entire mailing list with class schedule + offer</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Social media announcement scheduled for 5 days, 3 days, 1 day, day-of</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Press contacts confirmed who's covering opening</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Partner businesses notified of opening; cross-promotion live</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Music playlist tested in studio sound system at performance volume</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Cleaning checklist for opening day printed and posted</div></li>
</ul>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">Day of</span>
<h2 class="h2">Grand opening day</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Owner + entire staff arrive 90 minutes before doors open</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Final cleaning walkthrough — locker rooms, mirrors, equipment, floors</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Music + AV systems on; sound check at member-presence volume</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Refreshments staged; member-welcome table set up</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Each instructor runs through their class flow once</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>AI agent verified live for inbound lead response; test message confirmed</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Payment processing tested with a real transaction</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Press reminders sent to invited media</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Owner personally greets each founding member arriving</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>Photographer captures: first class, member moments, owner-with-team</div></li>
<li class="check-item"><div class="check-box"></div><div>End-of-day debrief with full team: what worked, what to fix tomorrow</div></li>
</ul>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">Days 1-30 post-open</span>
<h2 class="h2">The critical first month</h2>
<p class="body">The metrics that matter daily for the first 30 days post-open:</p>
<ul class="ul">
<li><strong>Daily member check-ins</strong> — Is utilization rising or falling? Which classes are filling? Which are empty?</li>
<li><strong>New member signups</strong> — Conversion of opening-week tours and inbound leads</li>
<li><strong>Cancellations and freezes</strong> — Any concerning early churn?</li>
<li><strong>Payment failures</strong> — Track + recover within 48 hours</li>
<li><strong>NPS / member feedback</strong> — Casual asks at check-in + a formal pulse at day 21</li>
<li><strong>Class capacity hit rates</strong> — Which classes need more sessions; which need fewer</li>
<li><strong>Lead-to-tour-to-member funnel</strong> — Validate the AI agent + sales motion working</li>
<li><strong>Cleanliness audits</strong> — Daily for first 30 days; member-experience makes or breaks early word-of-mouth</li>
</ul>
<div class="callout"><p><strong>The first 30 days predict the first year.</strong> A member's first 30 days at a gym predict their 12-month retention more than anything that follows. Over-invest in onboarding now; you'll be paid back in lower churn for the life of the membership.</p></div>
</div></section>

